<dd>
<p><b>FileNameArray (variable):
</b>A null-terminated string that specifies the name of the file in <span><a href="831cd729-be7c-451e-b729-bd8d84ce4d24#gt_c305d0ab-8b94-461a-bd76-13b40cb8c4d8" data-linktype="relative-path">Unicode</a></span>
<span><a href="831cd729-be7c-451e-b729-bd8d84ce4d24#gt_69864bcc-33be-41c9-9486-e18618ee3dd0" data-linktype="relative-path">UTF-16LE</a></span>
characters. The location of this buffer is determined by the value of the <b>FileNameOffset</b>
field.</p>
